{"tid":2401611,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"全世界學緊支那用數碼愚民主義統治","createTime":"2021-02-10T01:03:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-10T10:21:02.000Z","uid":113951,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"8ca1cd923002918d8686902a1a80f330118298de","tid":2401611,"uid":113951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T01:03:16.000Z","msg":"到底移民去邊先避得開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果「短視頻」平台只是在大陸入面流行，那於人類文明而言又實在無所謂，誰會理地獄鬼國內的人看甚麼? 但大陸公司，像微信和支付寶，經常改個名稱就去國際市場作文化侵略。<br />\n<br />\n中國公司一如既往，向全世界輸出數碼獨裁工具概念和實踐方法。例如早時的微信Mega App和最近的央行數碼貨幣(CBDC，Central Bank Digital Currency)。<br />\n<br />\n「短視頻」和內容演算法餵食的Dark Pattern，是一種破壞額葉運作的數碼毒品。這種數碼愚民政策，讓美國Big Tech都在抄襲和推出類似的功能和產品，例如Youtube的Shots和Instagram的Reels。<br />\n<br />\n深層國家統治的美國，配合有如1984的真理部的言論審查機制，根本是將整套用數碼毒品破壞思考能力，再以選擇性虛假消息洗腦的愚民統治方法，在中共於鬼國實驗成功後，照搬到美國。<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://mewe.com/p/blackmirrortech/show/601e06303fa4830cf8e3a867\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmewe.com%2Fp%2Fblackmirrortech%2Fshow%2F601e06303fa4830cf8e3a867&d=%2BlEHcpGCWp7P1IX%2BOWqMQtey%2FoW3U1ZMpR7BmJTbZh4%3D&h=86acc2e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mewe.com/p/blackmirrortech/show/601e06303fa4830cf8e3a867</a>"},{"pid":"ff0988423ba2c011828dccc9fcbd3f3b2330ff5e","tid":2401611,"uid":113951,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T01:06:52.000Z","msg":"呢條link先岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://mewe.com/p/blackmirrortech/show/6022a7457a916f575436ea0f\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmewe.com%2Fp%2Fblackmirrortech%2Fshow%2F6022a7457a916f575436ea0f&d=%2BlEHcpGCWp7P1IX%2BOWqMQtey%2FoW3U1ZMpR7BmJTbZh4%3D&h=9acd0f7b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mewe.com/p/blackmirrortech/show/6022a7457a916f575436ea0f</a>"},{"pid":"d2380e74f80169c84f3ae525029e5429ac4de8f0","tid":2401611,"uid":155095,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,